@tchalamet and @kyliejenner are making the most of their sporty summer. Today, the pair were spotted at #WorldCupFinal between Argentina and Spain in New Jersey, where Chalamet had the honour of delivering the official match ball before kick-off.
Elsewhere, @madonna shared the spotlight with football icons Ronaldinho and Ronaldo, while @shakira, @lilbieber and #BTS took to the stage for the tournament’s first-ever halftime show. Tom Cruise also made a surprise appearance as part of the pre-match festivities.
